      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks that helps. so when you say they're \"less developed,\" is that mostly because of their technology, or is there something more inherent about how those tribal or collectivist societies actually function compared to the modern ones? like, is there a reason why they haven't transitioned into the modern model?",
